subSubSection.paragraph:
The specimens described herein were collected at depths of 6-12 m from southern Taiwan. This species has been recorded in shallow waters of 1-20 m depth from the southern tip of Taiwan, Ryukyu Islands, Japan, Philippines, Sri Lanka, Australia, Thailand, Indonesia, Timor Sea, Papua New Guinea, Solomon Islands, Vanuatu, Fiji, Kiribati, and Line Islands (
Fricke 1997
).
